      "updated": 1782543517285,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "S3 like object storage",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "S3 like object storage",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "e5JizvRr7l9hvqCUG9jh4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 254.78302001953125,
      "y": 234.51251220703125,
      "width": 406.81561279296875,
      "height": 1120,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5a",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1447898098,
      "version": 818,
      "versionNonce": 2094214002,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782544184434,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Questions :\n\n1. S3 like object storage with objects and metadata\nyes\n\n2. imp features?\nUpload object\nCreate bucket\nList objects in a bucket\ndownload oject\nsee version history\n\n3. Scale?\n10m DAU\n\n4. file size?\nranges from kbs to GBs\n\n5. average storage per user ?\n10 gb\n\n6. API interface?\nyes\n\nFunc Requirements :\nUpload object\nCreate bucket\nList objects in a bucket\ndownload oject\nsee version history\n\nNFR:\nAvaialbility : SLA 99.9\nDurability : SLA 99.999999999\navailability > consistency\nHuge scale and global system\nlow latency\n\nBack of the envelope calculations:\n\n10m DAU\n\nTraffic :\nwrites\n10 m * 2 / 100,000 = 10^7 * 2 / 10^5 = 200 rps\nreads \n100:1\n200 * 100 = 20000 rps\n\nStorage :\n10m DAU * 10gb \n1 b total * 10 gb = 10^3 * 10 pb = 10000 pb\n\n30% small files : < 1mb\n50% medium : 1mb to 1 gb\n20% large files : > gb",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Questions :\n\n1. S3 like object storage with objects and metadata\nyes\n\n2. imp features?\nUpload object\nCreate bucket\nList objects in a bucket\ndownload oject\nsee version history\n\n3. Scale?\n10m DAU\n\n4. file size?\nranges from kbs to GBs\n\n5. average storage per user ?\n10 gb\n\n6. API interface?\nyes\n\nFunc Requirements :\nUpload object\nCreate bucket\nList objects in a bucket\ndownload oject\nsee version history\n\nNFR:\nAvaialbility : SLA 99.9\nDurability : SLA 99.999999999\navailability > consistency\nHuge scale and global system\nlow latency\n\nBack of the envelope calculations:\n\n10m DAU\n\nTraffic :\nwrites\n10 m * 2 / 100,000 = 10^7 * 2 / 10^5 = 200 rps\nreads \n100:1\n200 * 100 = 20000 rps\n\nStorage :\n10m DAU * 10gb \n1 b total * 10 gb = 10^3 * 10 pb = 10000 pb\n\n30% small files : < 1mb\n50% medium : 1mb to 1 gb\n20% large files : > gb",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
